# DO NOT use VITE_-prefixed env vars for secrets. They are bundled into client-side JS
# and visible in devtools/Network tab by anyone who loads the app.
#
# This app uses GitHub's unauthenticated rate limit (60 req/hr/IP).
# For a higher limit, add a server-side proxy (e.g. Vercel/Netlify function)
# that holds the token privately and exposes a /api/github/* route.
#
# GITHUB_TOKEN=your_token_here  (server-side only — never VITE_GITHUB_TOKEN)
